xmlText.p: German authorities seek information from Deutsche Bank in relation to Danske Bank
FRANKFURT, Sept 25 (Reuters) - German authorities have been seeking information at Deutsche Bank's Frankfurt headquarters in relation to Danske Bank, Frankfurt prosecutors said on Wednesday.
Deutsche Bank said it was cooperating.
(Reporting by Hans Seidenstuecker, Patricia Uhlig and Tom Sims; editing by Thomas Seythal)
